  fiber: 4 g
  sodium: 1730 mg
author: HelloFresh
cuisine: North America
servings: 2
course: main course
time required: 35 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/bachans-r-bbq-cheddar-pork-burgers-674e23f2f546e01c8f27738a
